A sermon preached before the Kings Most Excellent Majesty at Oxford by H.K., D.D. Killigrew, Henry, 1613-1700. King, Henry, 1592-1669.
[21] p. : port.
Printed for W. Web, Oxford : 1643.
Attributed to Henry Killigrew by BM and Halkett & Laing (2nd ed.); also attributed to Henry King. Place of publication and authorship in some doubt. Cf. Madan. This item identified at reel 35:17 as Wing K503 (number cancelled in Wing CD-ROM, 1996), and at reel 243:E.93, no. 13 as Wing (CD-ROM, 1996) K445. Reproduction of original in British Library and Thomason Collection, British Library.
